_sText:
I spent some time doing this map so I think you like it :)
Map based on de_inferno. Map made for the GunGame. 

Informations:

- Color Correction
- HDR
- Cubemaps
- Minimap
- env_sun
- 3d Skybox
- 64 spawns 
- optimalization
- .bsp size: 50mb

If you find a bug, report it in the comments or pw. Please comment and rate.

Have fun!


**If you've downloaded the map April 30, please download the new version.**
